# ðŸŽ¯ Cross-Site Scripting (XSS) Lab

## ðŸ“‹ Overview
XSS allows attackers to inject malicious scripts into web pages viewed by other users.

## ðŸ”¬ Types Explored
1. **Reflected XSS** - Non-persistent, appears in URL/response
2. **Stored XSS** - Persistent, saved in database
3. **DOM-based XSS** - Client-side manipulation

